headline: Crown Castle: 32% Dividend Cut, Falling Price, But Is It Actually A Bargain Or Value Trap?
summary: Despite long-term potential from focusing on U.S. towers, Crown Castle (CCI) trades at a premium to peers AMT and SBAC. See more here.
